{"type": "article", "id": 23355, "title": "上厕所思考人生，洗完手看动画片 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "碎片时间争分夺秒，然后一整天都在摸鱼……", "date": "2016-03-06T08:00:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 156, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125848Z0ELJG8YtqvQf974.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。<b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. Deadline 最后一小时写的比前一天都多。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021258391D0RgXwYHVs5ZEja.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 打游戏趁人物复活时间赶快写两笔作业。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021258417nBy2YrDS9FZe8Ks.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69387755\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 节省时间不做饭点外卖，然后花半小时思考吃什么外卖。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125841nmYGdK7qtQCaz980.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 边吃肉夹馍边打字，然后吃完瞌睡 20 分钟。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125842IQ7uTcHbStsLygKn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 订闹钟 6 点起床学习，然后迷迷糊糊到 9 点。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125843U6g0mwdeCLNHbDfr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 坚持不睡多工作半小时，然后第二天睡到 12 点。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125844VBSI0R4CwODJUgLu.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81578947\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7 .趁上厕所思考下人生状态，洗完手继续看动画片。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021258453jlCDxyMAa84UfiO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.068\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 坐地铁的时候研究经济学，到家继续看动画片。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125846QC25UHicOtXPDh8f.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 等红绿灯的时候回 10 条朋友圈。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125846bPwM17eok0SKtEC9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56315789\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>10. 因为别人慢了 5 分钟气到炸，然后磨蹭半小时思考怎么弥补回来。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021258477DsExHno3aRtFYpr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.418\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 工作时间刷淘宝从来不看评论和买家秀。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125848aHyGwKhMkxCsbmOg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</i><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">动图来自：<a href=\"http://giphy.com/gifs/girl-deal-with-it-movie-1tdFHS5vi4txK\">giphy.com</a></p>\n\n\n"}